name: Stickman Fight Multicraft
description:
Try to kill other stickman opponents and be the leader in the room.
You can collect golden apple and buy weapons , armors and a lot of things that you can use for multicraft.
** STICKMAN FIGHT CRAFT FEATURES **
• A lot of pixel weapons
• Amazing graphics
• Amazing sounds
• So much armors and hats
• Realistic animation with multicraft
• Perfect ragdoll physics
